2003-07-31  Michael Meeks  <michael@ximian.com>

	* Version 2.3.6
	
	* configure.in: require ORBit2 >= 2.7.5 for the is_a fix.

	* bonobo/bonobo-foreign-object.c
	(bonobo_foreign_object_new): add the CORBA_Object_is_a
	check back in.

	* bonobo/bonobo-object.c (do_corba_setup_T):
	move inheritance trap here, where we have a valid
	object reference.

