	(get_tmpdir): use ORBit_get_temp_dir, and fail noisly
	if we can't get a secure place to poke.
	(local_activator): force a local loop.

	* bonobo/bonobo-object.c: add linc locking dummies.

	* bonobo-activation/bonobo-activation-fork-server.c
	(bonobo_activation_server_by_forking): add 'use_new_loop'
	argument; create either an inferior loop, or use the
	glib mainloop - as suits. Only scan with the mainloop.
	(scan_list): use the mainloop here too.
	
	* tests/test-activation/bonobo-activation-test.c
	(race_empty): use g_main_iteration.

